{"tid":1578890,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"週末要人週末要人週末要人！！！！！","createTime":"2019-09-18T10:23:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-18T16:58:07.000Z","uid":266935,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"7abe8414129f54a7d7aa834b4cbb4ee2d4dd33bb","tid":1578890,"uid":266935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T10:23:37.000Z","msg":"如題，宜家香城online局勢陷入僵局，對我地一班抗爭者黎講已經進化到完全體，但好需要係十一前變究極體同支共死過<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咁我地去到呢個地步應該點做呢？我再次希望拋磚引玉，等連仔女們諗下<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n第一，和你塞進化。831有無死人我唔知，我都唔想有手足甚至平民出事，但當黨鐵繼續企係強權一方嘅時候，有需要將行動升級，由跳閘改成十八區黨鐵站公祭。<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />今個星期日我未見有大型活動(可能miss左無睇 sor<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)，假若無的話，可以動員所有人到自己區內嘅黨鐵做公祭，入站做也好，站外擺花也好，務求令831事件繼續spread，將最update嘅文宣貼係黨鐵度，公祭好重要，做完之後當然最重要係令每個黨鐵站迫滿人但又唔入閘喇，夠膽未封站囉。封站仲好，間接將被封站嘅手足迫去另一個站封另一個站<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />記住，我個人唔建議做漫無目的嘅行為，所以十八區公祭有兩個好重要嘅目的。第一個就係迫黨鐵交出所有與831有關嘅影片、文件。<br />\n<br />\n第二個目的就係迫林奠作出回應。大家係咪忘記左佢仲係特首？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />講真去發夢已經聽少左大家講佢嘅威水史。佢係特首，香港乜野狗屎垃圾都應該關佢事，831死人你地唔做佢？十日被自殺十幾二十人你地唔圍攻佢？我強烈要求所有記者或任何人有機會問佢野嘅時候只提一句:831係咪死左人請林女士交代<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />反正你問佢乜政治問題都好佢淨係答廢話，倒不如借發問機會spread開我地想大眾關注嘅訊息<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />同時間迫佢作為一國之首要回應市民<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />請大家緊記，狗隻只係我地凝聚社會嘅一個大因素，還擊唔應該淨係還落狗身上，成個政府先係最需要擊潰嘅對象<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nP.S. 何妖吹雞921要清潔大行動，我極不建議大家硬碰，唔係示弱，而係保存實力，呢啲用錢買嘅行動力搵鬼信咩，攞黎俾共狗爪牙claim行動費同圍爐咋嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />如果為左硬碰要折損手足就有啲唔抵，明知班狗偏幫嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a994b1b0bf1d5dba3b13381971691e25f95a26fa","tid":1578890,"uid":117906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T10:23:44.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">全球響應「929全球集會抗赤納粹」</span></span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">全世界一齊對準極權！</span></span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1577380\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1577380</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hWqVmOV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhWqVmOV.jpg&h=075c7745&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/n1tov9s.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fn1tov9s.png&h=0af09f95&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6d609cae814b00d6e4ea06137fc8151182e9816d","tid":1578890,"uid":266935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T10:23:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"41accb44bb5693809a8ff5f3b4bc6c73a378830e","tid":1578890,"uid":266935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T10:24:04.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"074101273da269d54aa8f7fb8dd4c59c5237d236","tid":1578890,"uid":266935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T10:24:28.000Z","msg":"推爆"},{"pid":"f7edfe2560168d07eccaa9969bce2353bff25795","tid":1578890,"uid":266935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T10:25:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0165426883226aae296f8db33aa448c49bf3067a","tid":1578890,"uid":266935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T10:25:30.000Z","msg":"由獅子山推到大老山"},{"pid":"38db98c5bd6e2f231cb